      "value": "<p>You can consume the latent magical charge of spell gems to fuel your own magical reservoir</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Ability to cast 3rd level spells</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Once per day as a full action you can destroy a spell gem you are holding to consume the magical energies within to regain a spent spell slot. The spell slot regained must be 2 levels lower than the spell level contained within the consumed spell gem.</p>"
